#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{	std::ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
	int t,i,j,n;
	cin>>t;
	for(i=1;i<=t;i++)
	{
		cin>>n;
		int a[n],res=0,frg=0;
		for(j=0;j<n;j++)
		{
			cin>>a[j];
			res+=(a[j]/30+1)*10;
			frg+=(a[j]/60+1)*15;	
		}
		if(res==frg)
		cout<<"Case "<<i<<": Respawn Frag "<<frg<<"\n";
		else if(res<frg)
		cout<<"Case "<<i<<": Respawn "<<res<<"\n";
		else
		cout<<"Case "<<i<<": Frag "<<frg<<"\n";
	}
	return 0;
}
